The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, Lagos State chapter, has relocated its secretariat to a more spacious location.

The party’s Publicity Secretary Mr. Hakeem Amode who gave the hint in a statement today, noted that the PDP Lagos relocated it’s secretariat from Adekunle Fajuyi GRA Ikeja, the new secretariat is now at 132b, Agege Motor road, Old Abeokuta Road, next to Total filling Station, at Zik Bus Stop.

According to Amode the relocation was due to a need for a place that could better accommodate the various units of the party’s functionaries in the secretariat.

He added that going forward all   correspondence are to be directed to the new address and  that all party activities will take place at the new secretariat.



